cc:Work.dc:title: Part - Linkage
cc:Work.dc:description:
Model for trying out linkages
Needs pins of length 2 and 3 times thickness as vitamins. Plain pins of length 2, Pins of length 3 with a disc on the first and middle third. Linkages more complicated than a four bar linkage might need even more pins variants.
Created with Boxes.py (https://boxes.hackerspace-bamberg.de/) Command line: boxes Linkage Command line short: boxes Linkage
